12:57.000Z","msg":"extraordinary claims need extraordinary evidence.<br />\n呢個唔止係科學原則，而係求證原則。<br />\n唔單止係科學，也係哲學和人文原則。"},{"pid":"1d7de145ac08e0a22caf5a5a22d531cd6b1fa9be","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-29T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J-Yg9N-q0Ok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ-Yg9N-q0Ok&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2J4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=52324f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J-Yg9N-q0Ok</a>"},{"pid":"0f3c66a268eb30becde4937a0d751a64d7e99c75","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea987f467afc8c3ee9306196e215ad0c741f1b14","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe314171be7d6e77e17ae61c9e550e2008517021","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f7839ef3c569aaabd1ca1ce2c908fd62f3395a","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95abbf84734a4b0c643ad4960c45a2647dcd2598","tid":2459926,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b816f299cdabd3ca09d725fa5e11c61ef4c9e643","tid":2459926,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"983980bf4d13a0c9d3588b2dfbf0bb48eb664af8","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"人類的科技研發，是用數理，科學方法去造福人類<br />\n<br />\n科學方法用數量，單位，實驗，計算為基礎<br />\n<br />\n對於科學至尊主義的人來說，他們追求的褔樂是用什麼單位去計算呢，甚麼量度這&ldquo;福樂&rdquo;呢？<br />\n<br />\n追求這種不能被量度，沒有單位，又沒有公式去計算的東西，對他們來說，會不會好荒謬呢？<br />\n<br />\n是不是應該找個方法去解釋&ldquo;苦樂&rdquo;去完整補足科學至上主義的這一個paradox呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"好似去到molecular level係有辦法量度到你所講的情感快樂的。<br />\n<br />\n就算用社會科學方法都可以玩問卷啦，啊文科撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"之前都係咁諗 但最近睇緊羅素D書<br />\n如果單純快樂就 = 腦內某幾種神經物質分泌<br />\n觀察到既物理現象係因定係果並唔重要 重要我還原呢個物理現象係咪就可以代表快樂(例子 毒品) <br />\n<br />\n我地一直都係用物理去解釋精神現象其實同感情既本質無咩關係 所謂本質應該係更直觀先可以理解到 問人咩叫幸福可以好簡單咁講到 但亦可以永世都比唔到一個universal既答案<br />\n<br />\n物理主義可以Handle Fact呢一面 但Value呢一面物理主義無處理到Value <br />\n<br />\n心理學同神經科學都Apply 自然科學研究方法<br />\n但呢個世界某D對於Value唔重要既現象黎講 <br />\n單純科學就足以解釋所有野 例如重力 / 數學<br />\n但現象涉及人類就涉及到Value科學就只係單純一個Perspective  BTW我亦都唔係講緊乜野超自然既野 只係純粹用現象學同存在主義去睇番感情係咩一回事"},{"pid":"478beef85e26b15575b56a64750dba9f4ad36e41","tid":2459926,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b1ecaaa43a025eb3d4a2e716dcccdd3bb3fb81","tid":2459926,"uid":290527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f895d60113c701f543bd0eb968cd9953e3d98b","tid":2459926,"uid":290527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}